args:
The group defeats Xuan Zang, but she refuses
to give up trying to seal Mei Hou Wang. This
makes Wu Kong lose his temper and destroy
the Jin Gu Er, which releases a dark power
that restores Mei Hou Wang's memories of
the time when he despised mortals.
Damn, that Xihe thingy is no joke!
*pant* It would be dangerous to use Xihe's\npower further...but I cannot give up.
I understand your desire to be kind in this\nmatter—truly I do. But it simply cannot be.
It is the duty of a sealer to handle\nQilin relics and seal away danger.
Duty is no excuse to hurt someone\nwho's done nothing wrong!
Unless doing so means averting many\npotential crises in the future.
And I can do naught but give every ounce\nof myself to fulfilling my mission. Haaaah!
Well, THIS is not good. I fear the master\nintends to unleash the entirety of the\nXihe's considerable power.
Yeah, she's done playin' games.\nSo what's the plan?
All right, master! If you're gonna try to\nseal my friend up no matter what,\nthen you leave me no choice...
Wu Kong, wait! What are you doing\nwith the Jin Gu Er?!
Making it so she can't seal Mei Hou Wang\nno matter WHAT she does. Hah!
You broke the thing! ...Can you DO that?!

You FOOL! That was a precious relic
wrought and wrangled from the marvels
of the Qilin's engineering prowess,
and now it's...it's...
You can't seal Mei Hou Wang away,\nso what are you gonna do?
It's gushing up from the Jin Gu Er!
He looks to be in pain.
Hey, you okay, buddy? You got really—
That black...whatever it is is heading\nright for Mei Hou Wang!
Stay back, all of you!\nDo not approach!
Yes, but I just felt an incredible\npower pass overhead...
I have returned to this world\noverflowing with power!
Uh, Mei Hou Wang? Is that you?\nWhat's with your body?
It is all thanks to you, Wu Kong.
Because you released the last bit of my\nremaining power from the Jin Gu Er,\nI have returned to my original form!
I remember everything! Every memory of\nwanting to wipe all of you foul, mewling,\nmortals from the face of the earth!
No! What the heck's gotten into you?!
I recognize that you have fostered\na bond of sorts with Mei Hou Wang.
However, this occurred during a period\nin which he lacked his true memories.
With his memory returned, he is another\nbeast entirely. You must accept that the\nsoul you thought you knew is gone.
She's right, Wu Kong.\nYou need to stay back.
Don't tell me YOU'RE gonna fight him now!
You saw what he did. How strong he is.\nIf we don't stop him now, he could rain\ndestruction down on everything.
Don't worry, my man—we're just gonna\ntire him out so he can't fight anymore.
Truce, Xuan Zang? Or can we at least\nput our differences aside until we stop\nthis greater threat?
I welcome your aid, for I will not be able\nto keep his power in check by myself\nnow that he is unchained.
Are you deciding which of you dies first?\nI assure you, it is a meaningless question.
FOR YOU WILL ALL DIE NOOOOOW!
